We have to find them, quick.

17
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,320
Let's go.

18
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,360
Xiao Heyan.

19
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,800
Xiao Heyan.

20
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:17,720
Wake up.

21
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:18,800
Wake up.

22
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:21,920
Are you okay?

23
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,000
Dr. Ji,

24
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,370
we've been looking for you for so long.

25
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:32,960
Chuyun.

26
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,040
You betrayed us.

27
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,360
You...

28
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,680
I did it.

29
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,040
I did it.

30
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:58,960
I did it.

31
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,200
Dr. Ji,

32
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,880
I did it.

33
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,400
Take this whistle.

34
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,400
Du Yu planted a poisonous bug in Yan Quezuo, too.

35
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,280
You can use this whistle

36
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,360
to control him.

37
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,560
I just removed the bug.

38
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,560
But he might still be dangerous.

39
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,120
Watch him for me.

40
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,860
I'm going to gather herbs.

41
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,120
Don't worry.

42
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,360
Ji Bai,

43
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,880
where are you going?

44
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,120
Where is the Heir?

45
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,800
Do you think that whistle can save your life?

46
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,480
Yan Quezuo killed them.

47
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,000
Quick!

48
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,380
As long as I kill Ji Bai,

49
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,600
I won't lose control anymore.

50
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,480
Get him!

51
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,400
Master.

52
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,400
What audacious fellow

53
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,600
dares to bully my disciple?

54
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,240
Lord Yan.

55
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,280
You...

56
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,700
Why are you doing this?

57
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,450
She is the Young Master's fiancée.

58
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,820
Elder Zhou,

59
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,360
you have been deceived by him all along.

60
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:20,160
In fact, under the guise of seeking justice for General Shen,

61
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,560
he used poisonous insects to control Xiao Heyan,

62
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,680
coerced the Northern Zhen Manor,

63
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,320
and plotted treason.

64
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,120
What?

65
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,000
Get them!

66
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,320
Take him away.

67
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,400
Get up.

68
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:57,880
Master,

69
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,210
why are you here?

70
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,560
Didn't you write to me about the poisonous insects?

71
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,960
I thought I would come to see you.

72
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,640
Please come with me quickly.

73
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,240
Only you can save Xiao Heyan.

74
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,330
Let's go.

75
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,840
Yan Quezuo,

76
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,000
for the crimes you committed,

77
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,120
I cannot shield you.

78
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,480
I will hand you over to the authorities

79
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,280
and let them deal with you by law.

80
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,200
The winner takes all.

81
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,920
Kill me or cut me to pieces.

82
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,159
Do with me as you wish.

83
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,040
Take him away.

84
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:46,680
Now that General Shen's orphan has been found,

85
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,880
my mission is complete.

86
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:49,480
I plan to close the Escort Agency

87
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,610
and lead everyone back to the Capital.

88
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,680
Please rise.

89
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,680
Young Master.

90
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,450
I leave him in your care.

91
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,440
You must help him wake up.

92
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,000
He is my husband.

93
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,000
Naturally, I will take good care of him.

94
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,120
If you want to see him in the future,

95
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,380
you can come to Gushan.

96
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,320
Chuyun.

97
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,360
Do you want to return to Gushan with me?

98
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,840
My master and I

99
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:24,970
can definitely cure the poisonous insects in your body.

100
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,000
I...

101
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,800
I see you are well-behaved and sensible,

102
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,240
and you have a special constitution.

103
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:33,520
Why not become my closed-door disciple?

104
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,460
What do you say?

105
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,200
Can I really?

106
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,280
Of course.

107
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,380
I, Chuyun, pay my respects to Master.

108
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,600
Ji Bai.

109
