117
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:34,039
Whether he wakes up or not,

118
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,840
I've made up my mind.

119
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,679
I'll take care of him for the rest of my life.

120
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,480
Ji...

121
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,960
Ji Bai.

122
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:09,840
You're finally awake.

123
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:14,680
I had a very, very long dream.

124
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:19,320
I dreamt of my father,

125
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,880
